(80, 'PH747666', 'Past Questions on General Basic Inorganic Chemistry ICH 111 (150 Questions & Answers)', '<p>Past Questions on General Basic Inorganic Chemistry ICH 111 (150 Questions &amp; Answers) is a carefully compiled resource designed to help students excel in their Industrial Chemistry courses. This exam prep material covers a wide range of essential topics in ICH 111, including atomic structure, periodic table trends, chemical bonding, gas laws, stoichiometry, redox reactions, acids and bases, and properties of matter.</p>\r\n<p>With 150 well-structured multiple-choice questions and detailed answers, this question bank is ideal for practice, revision, and self-assessment. It is suitable for students preparing for mid-semester tests, final exams, or university entrance assessments in chemistry-related programs.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re looking to reinforce your understanding or test your exam readiness, this comprehensive guide provides the support you need to build confidence and achieve academic success in General Basic Inorganic Chemistry.</p>', '<p>This question bank contains 150 multiple-choice questions and answers for General Basic Inorganic Chemistry (ICH 111). It is designed to help students prepare effectively for exams by covering key topics such as atomic structure, chemical bonding, periodic table trends, gas laws, and acids &amp; bases. Ideal for revision and self-assessment.</p>', '', '', '1', 'Year 1', '19', '5', 'Yes', 13, 174, 'paid', 2000, 'Past Questions on General Basic Inorganic Chemistry ICH 111 (150 Questions & Answers)', 1, 5, '2025-05-27 23:57:55', '2025-05-27 23:57:55', 'approved', 'past-questions-on-general-basic-inorganic-chemistry-ich-111-150-questions-answers'),
(81, 'PH341135', 'Crack ICH 111: Inorganic Chemistry Past Questions with Answers (150 Questions & Answers)', '<p>Crack ICH 111: Inorganic Chemistry Past Questions with Answers is your essential exam prep resource for mastering General Basic Inorganic Chemistry.</p>\r\n<p>This comprehensive guide features a carefully selected collection of past questions, each with clear and accurate answers to help you test your understanding, reinforce key concepts, and build confidence.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Covering core areas such as atomic structure, periodicity, chemical bonding, stoichiometry, and properties of gases and acids, this book is perfect for students preparing for ICH 111 exams. Whether you\'re aiming to revise or sharpen your problem-solving skills, this resource is your key to success.</p>', '<p>Crack ICH 111: Inorganic Chemistry Past Questions with Answers is a comprehensive exam prep tool featuring 150 well-structured questions and solutions.</p>\r\n<p>Designed to help students master core topics in General Basic Inorganic Chemistry, this guide is ideal for effective revision and academic success.</p>', '', '', '1', 'Year 1', '19', '5', 'Yes', 13, 174, 'paid', 2000, 'Crack ICH 111: Inorganic Chemistry Past Questions with Answers', 1, 5, '2025-05-28 00:48:42', '2025-05-28 00:48:42', 'approved', 'crack-ich-111-inorganic-chemistry-past-questions-with-answers-150-questions-answers'),
(82, 'PH794204', 'Your ICH 111 Success Pack: Inorganic Chemistry Past Questions & Answers (150 Questions & Answers)', '<p>Your ICH 111 Success Pack: Inorganic Chemistry Past Questions &amp; Answers is your ultimate companion for mastering General Basic Inorganic Chemistry.</p>\r\n<p>This resource features 150 carefully selected objective questions with detailed answers, tailored to reflect real exam formats.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re preparing for tests, revising key concepts, or assessing your understanding, this pack provides the clarity and confidence you need to excel in ICH 111. Ideal for both self-study and group revision.</p>', '<p>Ace your ICH 111 exam with this Success Pack featuring 150 past questions and answers in General Basic Inorganic Chemistry&mdash;perfect for quick revision and confident preparation.</p>', '', '', '1', 'Year 1', '19', '5', 'Yes', 13, 174, 'paid', 2000, 'Your ICH 111 Success Pack: Inorganic Chemistry Past Questions & Answers (150 Questions & Answers)', 1, 5, '2025-05-28 09:49:46', '2025-05-28 09:49:46', 'approved', 'your-ich-111-success-pack-inorganic-chemistry-past-questions-answers-150-questions-answers'),
(83, 'PH056002', 'Ace ICH 111: Past Questions and Detailed Solutions (150 Questions & Answers)', '<p>Ace ICH 111: Past Questions and Detailed Solutions (150 Questions &amp; Answers) is your ultimate companion for mastering the fundamentals of Industrial Chemistry (ICH 111). Whether you\'re preparing for upcoming exams or revising key concepts, this comprehensive guide provides 150 carefully selected objective questions covering all major topics in the course.</p>\r\n<p>Each question is accompanied by clear, concise, and well-explained solutions, making it easy to understand the reasoning behind every correct answer. Designed for both quick revision and in-depth study, this resource helps you identify common exam patterns, boost your confidence, and improve your performance.</p>\r\n<p>What&rsquo;s Inside:</p>\r\n<p>150 past and practice questions based on real ICH 111 exam formats</p>\r\n<p>Detailed step-by-step explanations for every answer</p>\r\n<p>Coverage of key areas such as atomic structure, periodic table, chemical bonding, stoichiometry, states of matter, and more</p>\r\n<p>Ideal for students in science and engineering disciplines taking introductory chemistry courses</p>\r\n<p>Ace ICH 111 is perfect for university students, pre-degree science candidates, and anyone looking to solidify their foundational knowledge in chemistry.</p>', '<p>Ace ICH 111: Past Questions and Detailed Solutions offers 150 carefully selected multiple-choice questions with clear, step-by-step answers.</p>\r\n<p>Designed for quick revision and exam preparation, it covers key Industrial Chemistry topics to help you master ICH 111 with confidence.</p>', '', '', '1', 'Year 1', '19', '5', 'Yes', 13, 174, 'paid', 2000, 'Ace ICH 111: Past Questions and Detailed Solutions (150 Questions & Answers)', 1, 5, '2025-05-28 10:52:46', '2025-05-28 10:52:46', 'approved', 'ace-ich-111-past-questions-and-detailed-solutions-150-questions-answers'),
(84, 'PH752715', 'Test Your Knowledge: ICH 111 (General Basic Inorganic Chemistry) Past Exams with Expert Answers (150 questions & answers)', '<p>Test Your Knowledge: ICH 111 (General Basic Inorganic Chemistry) Past Exams with Expert Answers is a powerful study tool featuring 150 past exam questions and expert solutions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This resource is designed to help students sharpen their understanding, reinforce key concepts, and prepare effectively for ICH 111 exams. Each question comes with a clear, detailed answer, making it ideal for self-assessment and revision in General Basic Inorganic Chemistry. Perfect for science and engineering students aiming for academic excellence.</p>', '<p>Test Your Knowledge: ICH 111 offers 150 past exam questions with expert answers, covering key topics in General Basic Inorganic Chemistry. Perfect for quick revision and exam prep.</p>', '', '', '1', 'Year 1', '19', '5', 'Yes', 13, 174, 'paid', 2000, 'Test Your Knowledge: ICH 111 (General Basic Inorganic Chemistry) Past Exams with Expert Answers (150 questions & answers)', 1, 5, '2025-05-28 14:31:41', '2025-05-28 14:31:41', 'approved', 'test-your-knowledge-ich-111-general-basic-inorganic-chemistry-past-exams-with-expert-answers-150-questions-answers'),
(85, 'PH615576', 'Quick Revision for ICH 111 (General Basic Inorganic Chemistry): Solved Past Questions (150 Questions & Answers)', '<p>Quick Revision for ICH 111 (General Basic Inorganic Chemistry): Solved Past Questions is a comprehensive and student-friendly guide designed to help you prepare effectively for your ICH 111 exams.</p>\r\n<p>This book compiles a wide range of carefully selected past questions, each accompanied by clear, step-by-step solutions to enhance understanding and retention.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re reviewing the basics or tackling more complex concepts, this resource offers a quick and efficient way to revise key topics such as atomic structure, periodic trends, chemical bonding, stoichiometry, states of matter, acids and bases, and more. The solved questions are tailored to reflect actual exam formats, giving you a realistic practice experience.</p>\r\n<p>Key Features:</p>\r\n<p>Covers all essential topics in General Basic Inorganic Chemistry</p>\r\n<p>Includes numerous solved past questions with expert explanations</p>\r\n<p>Designed for quick revision, self-testing, and focused study</p>\r\n<p>Suitable for science and engineering students taking ICH 111</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for both last-minute cramming and thorough preparation, Quick Revision for ICH 111 is your trusted companion for mastering the fundamentals and excelling in your exams.</p>', '<p>Quick Revision for ICH 111 (General Basic Inorganic Chemistry): Solved Past Questions is your go-to guide for fast and effective exam preparation.</p>\r\n<p>It features a collection of carefully selected past questions with accurate, step-by-step solutions to help you grasp core concepts quickly. Ideal for last-minute revision and boosting your confidence before the exam.</p>', '', '', '1', 'Year 1', '19', '5', 'Yes', 13, 174, 'paid', 2000, 'Quick Revision for ICH 111 (General Basic Inorganic Chemistry): Solved Past Questions', 1, 5, '2025-05-28 16:33:12', '2025-05-28 16:33:12', 'approved', 'quick-revision-for-ich-111-general-basic-inorganic-chemistry-solved-past-questions-150-questions-answers'),
(86, 'PH690286', 'Basic Inorganic Chemistry Exam Workbook: ICH 111 Past Q&A (110 Questions & Answers)', '<p>Basic Inorganic Chemistry Exam Workbook: ICH 111 Past Q&amp;A (110 Questions &amp; Answers) is a comprehensive and practical study guide crafted to help students excel in the foundational course of Industrial Chemistry (ICH 111). This workbook features 110 well-curated multiple-choice questions, each drawn from past examination papers and designed to reflect the actual question patterns encountered in the course.</p>\r\n<p>Every question is accompanied by a clear, concise, and expertly written solution, making it easier for students to understand the core principles of General Basic Inorganic Chemistry. From atomic structure, periodic classification, chemical bonding, and stoichiometry to gas laws, acids and bases, and redox reactions, this workbook covers all key topics necessary for academic success.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re studying for a semester test, preparing for final exams, or simply reinforcing your understanding of fundamental inorganic chemistry concepts, this workbook offers an effective combination of practice, explanation, and review.</p>\r\n<p>Key Features:</p>\r\n<p>110 past exam questions with detailed, step-by-step answers</p>\r\n<p>Covers all major topics in ICH 111 (General Basic Inorganic Chemistry)</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for classroom use, independent study, and exam prep</p>\r\n<p>Builds problem-solving skills and reinforces conceptual understanding</p>\r\n<p>Suitable for science and engineering students at the university level</p>\r\n<p>With its student-focused approach, Basic Inorganic Chemistry Exam Workbook helps learners boost their confidence, improve their grades, and develop a strong foundation in inorganic chemistry. It is a must-have resource for anyone serious about succeeding in ICH 111.</p>', '<p>Basic Inorganic Chemistry Exam Workbook: ICH 111 Past Q&amp;A features 110 carefully selected past questions with detailed answers. It\'s the perfect tool for mastering key concepts in General Basic Inorganic Chemistry and preparing effectively for ICH 111 exams.</p>', '', '', '1', 'Year 1', '19', '5', 'Yes', 13, 174, 'paid', 1500, 'Basic Inorganic Chemistry Exam Workbook: ICH 111 Past Q&A (110 Questions & Answers)', 1, 5, '2025-05-28 17:44:55', '2025-05-28 17:44:55', 'approved', 'basic-inorganic-chemistry-exam-workbook-ich-111-past-q-a-110-questions-answers');

